Speaker 2: And clearly.

Speaker 1: Para Español, marque numero nueve.

Speaker 2: I had an order of packages and I never received it.

Speaker 2: And I did talk to the UPS man, they did text me back, I'm in the post office, and they tell me they delivered it on a Saturday and I ain't seen them.

Speaker 1: Thanks, transferring to agent.
